-al-qawl"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-3OF","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":480,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/31\/how-prophet-criticized-people\/","url_meta":{"origin":14673,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Manners: How the Prophet criticized people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 31, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would not insult others, he would not use profanity, and he would not curse others. If he wanted to criticize one of us, he would say, \"What is the matter with him? His forehead be dusted!\" Source: \u1e62a\u1e25\u012b\u1e25\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1993,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/24\/do-not-invoke-nar-jahannam\/","url_meta":{"origin":14673,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Curses: Do not invoke the Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Samurah ibn Jundab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not curse each other with the curse of Allah, nor invoke His wrath, nor invoke the Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1976 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi Imam Ibn \u2018Allan commented, \u201cHis saying \u2018nor invoke His\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11519,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/18\/do-not-curse-insult-sahabah\/","url_meta":{"origin":14673,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Do not curse companions of the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not insult my companions. If one of you were to spend the likes of mount Uhud in gold, it would not reach a small portion of theirs or even half of that.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3673,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41346,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/10\/04\/advise-not-to-curse\/","url_meta":{"origin":14673,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: I advise you not to curse others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Jurmuz al-Hujaymi reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, advise me.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI advise you not to curse others.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 20678 Grade:\u00a0Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani Imam al-Ghazali commented, \u201cClose to cursing is supplication for evil against a person, even\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26692,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/07\/03\/do-not-curse-the-dead\/","url_meta":{"origin":14673,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Death: Do not curse the dead, hurt the living","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Mughirah ibn Shu\u2019bah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not abuse the dead and thus harm the living.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1982 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani Imam al-San'ani commented, \"The prohibition of insulting the dead is general, including unbelievers or others.\"\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32160,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/not-befitting-believers-curse\/","url_meta":{"origin":14673,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: Not befitting believers to curse others","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believer is not in the habit of cursing others.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2019 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u0643\u064f\u0648\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u064f \u0644\u064e\u0639\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064b\u0627 2019 \u0633\u0646\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062a\